<font color="#FF0000">HELP'S ON THE WAY</font><br>
<tt>Fri Aug 29 21:34:22 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Silent Warrior:  Mustang Two Four is enroute.. Stopped off at the Marine Corps NCO Club and ripped off one of their pin ball machines.. duct taped it to the front of my attack lawn mower.. feels good to have a real cockpit around me.  Lowered my service ceiling to twenty three feet.. lost 5 knots airspeed (20%).<br>
Just passed over the Tote Lam Carwash... saw Cookie down there getting his gun cleaned... also his underwear and his M-60.<br>
Looks like Toon Sergeant Duke coming up at two o'clock...looks like he is spray painting some water buffalo..bright green... guess he figures that anything that pulls a plow ought to look like a John Deere..  Getting closer...Yep!..Its him alright...I can tell by the way he walks... has real weak knees, you know...that's where his athletes foot and jockey itch overlap! Seen one grunt...seen'em all!<br>
My ETA is shortly after the Big Air Strike... should narrow things down a bit for me... at least I'll know were the Commies weren't!<br>
Hey, Look! ...those Marines down there...they look just like ants...Holy Smoke!.. those are ants... I'm losing altitude.<br><br>
Mustang Two Four - Dustin' the jungle floor!
<p><code>-- getting there's half the fun  (Enroute or In roots) </code><p>


